data.description: Looking for the ideal home located in a great school district? Look no further! This home has many updates including new A/C in 2022, completely remodeled kitchen with open concept, new windows and blinds, new waterproof flooring, fresh paint inside and out. Backyard includes fenced-in dog run. Enjoy your morning coffee or watch the rain on the covered back patio. Garage door has a smart feature and can be opened remotely. Floored attic.
